    {
      "step_idx": 0,
      "role": "Local_Knowledge_Expert",
      "content": "You are given: (1) a task and advises from your manager with a specific plan and (2) a general task.\nCollect information from the general task, follow the suggestions from manager to solve the task.\n\n# General Task\nWhich gyms near Tompkins Square Park (<200m) have fitness classes before 7am? Please solve the task carefully.\n\n# Task and suggestions from manager\n## Task description\nIdentify gyms near Tompkins Square Park (<200m) that have fitness classes before 7am.\n\n## Plan for solving the task\n1. Identify Gyms Near Tompkins Square Park:\n   - Use a mapping service or database to find gyms within 200 meters of Tompkins Square Park.\n   \n2. Check Fitness Class Schedules:\n   - Visit the websites or contact the identified gyms to check their class schedules.\n   - Specifically look for classes that start before 7am.\n\n## Output format\n- List of gyms with their names and addresses.\n- Details of fitness classes that start before 7am including the type of class and the time it starts.\n\n## Constraints and conditions for completion\n- The gyms must be within 200 meters of Tompkins Square Park.\n- The fitness classes must start before 7am. "
    },
    {
      "step_idx": 1,
      "role": "Local_Knowledge_Expert",
      "content": "To start with the task, I'll need to identify gyms located within 200 meters of Tompkins Square Park. I will then check the schedules of these gyms to see if they have fitness classes that start before 7am.\n\nLet's begin by identifying the gyms within the specified radius.\n\nI'll use a mapping service to locate gyms within 200 meters of Tompkins Square Park. Here are some known mapping services and databases:\n- Google Maps\n- Yelp\n- Local business directories\n\nI'll start by identifying the coordinates of Tompkins Square Park and then find gyms within a 200-meter radius.\n\nThe coordinates of Tompkins Square Park are approximately:\nLatitude: 40.7265\nLongitude: -73.9815\n\nI'll now use these coordinates to find gyms within the specified radius.\n\nLet's proceed with identifying gyms within the specified area using a Python script to fetch this data.\n\n```python\nimport requests\n\n# Constants for Tompkins Square Park coordinates and radius\nLATITUDE = 40.7265\nLONGITUDE = -73.9815\nRADIUS = 200  # in meters\n\n# Function to fetch gyms within the specified radius\ndef get_nearby_gyms(latitude, longitude, radius):\n    url = \"https://maps.googleapis.com/maps/api/place/nearbysearch/json\"\n    params = {\n        \"location\": f\"{latitude},{longitude}\",\n        \"radius\": radius,\n        \"type\": \"gym\",\n        \"key\": \"YOUR_GOOGLE_MAPS_API_KEY\"  # Replace with your Google Maps API Key\n    }\n    response = requests.get(url, params=params)\n    return response.json()\n\n# Fetch gyms within the 200-meter radius of Tompkins Square Park\ngyms_data = get_nearby_gyms(LATITUDE, LONGITUDE, RADIUS)\ngyms = gyms_data.get(\"results\", [])\n\n# Print the names and addresses of the gyms\nfor gym in gyms:\n    name = gym.get(\"name\")\n    address = gym.get(\"vicinity\")\n    print(f\"Gym: {name}, Address: {address}\")\n```\n\nOnce we have the list of gyms, I'll proceed to check their class schedules for fitness classes before 7am. I'll need to visit their websites or contact them directly to get this information.\n\nLet's start by running the above code to get the list of gyms near Tompkins Square Park."
    },
