      "content": "Here is the plan to check the class schedules:\n\n1. **Blink Fitness**:\n   - Navigate to the class schedule section on the [Blink Fitness website](https://www.blinkfitness.com/).\n\n2. **TMPL**:\n   - Navigate to the class schedule section on the [TMPL website](https://www.tmplclubs.com/).\n\n3. **East Side Athletic Club**:\n   - Contact them directly to inquire about their class schedule.\n\n### Blink Fitness Class Schedule:\nI'll check the class schedules on the website for classes that start before 7am.\n\n### TMPL Class Schedule:\nI'll check the class schedules on the website for classes that start before 7am.\n\n### East Side Athletic Club:\nI'll call them to get the class schedule information.\n\nLet's manually review the schedules for Blink Fitness and TMPL online. I'll report the findings here. If any of these gyms have classes before 7am, I'll update accordingly."
